-- Easyknit International Sues Hong Kong Police, Seeks to Quash Search Order
-- Nipa Piboontanasawat
-- 2010-07-06T04:46:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-06/easyknit-international-sues-hong-kong-police-seeks-to-quash-search-order.html

          
          
             Easyknit International Holdings Ltd.
issued a writ of summons against the Hong Kong police, claiming
that they didn’t have “reasonable cause” for a search warrant,
the company said today in a statement to the Hong Kong stock
exchange.  
 Easyknit is seeking to quash the warrant and is seeking
damages and the return of seized documents, according to the
statement.  
          
          


  


        